This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image segmentation. The use of geometric priors also suggests that it may fall under the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of active learning techniques may suggest that it could also be classified under Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) or Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
